description: A family-owned truck specializing in delicious Guatemalan goodness, Blue Donkey Cafe is serving up something you're sure to love! With the finest tacos and black bean soup that Oklahoma City has ever seen, Blue Donkey is ready to make its mark on your daily lunch routine. Try the unique taste you won't find anywhere else, from the fantastic folks of Blue Donkey Cafe!
name: Blue Donkey Cafe
